    {
        "content": "<p>I think it's still syn1</p>",
        "id": 448836405,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1720010006
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>there should be a newer version</p>",
        "id": 448836451,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1720010018
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The one on GitHub seems newer but it's 1.0.104 still</p>",
        "id": 448836570,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1720010037
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>did you see <a href=\"https://github.com/ojeda/linux/tree/syn2benno\">https://github.com/ojeda/linux/tree/syn2benno</a></p>",
        "id": 448837206,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
