    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"690399\">@Lyude</span> I have updated my WIP to use Miguel's syn2 branch.<br>\n<span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"411477\">@Miguel Ojeda</span> I rebased your syn2 branch on top of rust-next and placed it in my fork's syn2 branch, feel free to take it</p>",
        "id": 453678359,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1721823463
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"413824\">Gary Guo</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/291566-Library/topic/Extending.20vtable.20macro.20to.20provide.20unique.20address/near/453678359\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"690399\">Lyude</span> I have updated my WIP to use Miguel's syn2 branch.<br>\n<span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"411477\">Miguel Ojeda</span> I rebased your syn2 branch on top of rust-next and placed it in my fork's syn2 branch, feel free to take it</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Thanks! I'll get to rebasing against it soon</p>",
        "id": 454010227,
        "sender_full_name": "Lyude",
        "timestamp": 1721928985
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Hm. Do you have any examples of how this would be used? I tried this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"sd\">/// The main trait for implementing the drm_plane API. This contains the various trait methods that</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">/// need to be implemented by a driver. The private driver data for the plane is contained in</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">/// whatever struct the driver defines which implements this trait.</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#[vtable]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">trait</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">DriverPlane</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Send</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Sync</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Sized</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[unique]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FUNCS</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"nb\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">drm_plane_funcs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">drm_plane_funcs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">update_plane</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">drm_atomic_helper_update_plane</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">disable_plane</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">drm_atomic_helper_disable_plane</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">destroy</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">plane_destroy_callback</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">reset</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">plane_reset_callback</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">set_property</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_duplicate_state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">atomic_duplicate_state_callback</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_destroy_state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">atomic_destroy_state_callback</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_set_property</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO someday</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_get_property</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO someday</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">late_register</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO someday</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">early_unregister</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO someday</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_print_state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO: Display someday???</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">format_mod_supported</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO someday</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[unique]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">HELPER_FUNCS</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"nb\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">drm_plane_helper_funcs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">drm_plane_helper_funcs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">prepare_fb</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">HAS_PREPARE_FB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">prepare_fb_callback</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">},</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">cleanup_fb</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">HAS_CLEANUP_FB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cleanup_fb_callback</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">},</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">begin_fb_access</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO: someday?</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">end_fb_access</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO: someday?</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_check</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">HAS_ATOMIC_CHECK</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">atomic_check_callback</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">},</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_update</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Some</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">atomic_update_callback</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_enable</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_disable</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_async_check</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">atomic_async_update</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// TODO</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">panic_flush</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">get_scanout_buffer</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">None</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// The data type to use for passing incoming arguments for new `Plane&lt;T&gt;` instances</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// Drivers which don't care about this can just use `()`</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Args</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// The parent driver implementation</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Driver</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">KmsDriver</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// The full type for this driver's drm_plane_state implementation. Drivers which don't need</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// special DRM helpers for their plane states may just use `PlaneState&lt;T&gt;` here, where `T` is</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// their private state struct which implements `DriverPlaneState`</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">State</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">PlaneStateHelper</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// Create the plane driver's private data structure</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">device</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Device</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Driver</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">args</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Args</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// The atomic check hook</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">atomic_check</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">plane</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Plane</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">new_state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">BorrowedPlaneState</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;'</span><span class=\"nb\">_</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">old_state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">AtomicStateComposer</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Driver</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">build_error</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">build_error</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"This should not be reachable\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// The atomic_update hook for this plane.</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">///</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// XXX: Currently not optional, but should be in the future once we add support for</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// atomic_enable/disable</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">atomic_update</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">plane</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Plane</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">new_state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">BorrowedPlaneState</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;'</span><span class=\"nb\">_</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">old_state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">AtomicStateMutator</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Driver</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// Callback for any work the driver needs to perform for preparing a framebuffer</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">prepare_fb</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">plane</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Plane</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">PlaneStateMutator</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;'</span><span class=\"nb\">_</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">build_error</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">build_error</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"This should not be reachable\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// Callback for any work the driver needs to perform for cleaning up a framebuffer that's no</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// longer in use. This should be the inverse of `prepare_fb()`</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">cleanup_fb</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">plane</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Plane</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">PlaneStateMutator</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;'</span><span class=\"nb\">_</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">State</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">build_error</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">build_error</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"This should not be reachable\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>But then if I try to implement <code>DriverPlane</code> on rvkms's side it tells me that I am missing implementations for FUNCS and HELPER_FUNCS, along with some of the other constants generated by <code>#[unique]</code></p>",
        "id": 456927055,
        "sender_full_name": "Lyude",
        "timestamp": 1722968965
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>you need to repeat the signature on the impl sidee</p>",
        "id": 456928435,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1722969474
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ah, gotcha. Is that something we might be able to fix? It's not a huge deal but I'd assume we'd rather avoid having to make users specify the type signature for a raw type in <code>bindings</code>... though I guess I could wrap those two things into a new type and use that</p>",
        "id": 456928588,
        "sender_full_name": "Lyude",
        "timestamp": 1722969535
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It's possible but I would need the associated_type_defaults unstable feature for it</p>",
        "id": 456928941,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1722969672
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>BTW - anything else you need from me? I tried this on my branch and it seems to work fine, would be happy to help review on the mailing list as well if you want (just make sure to CC me)</p>",
        "id": 469195350,
        "sender_full_name": "Lyude",
        "timestamp": 1725997498
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Well, the change currently depends on syn support...</p>",
        "id": 469195694,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1725997582
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>BTW - any updates on this/anything I can do to help push forward syn support and support for this in general?</p>",
