    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"413824\">@Gary Guo</span> I think there's been some more syn2 work going on for the kernel, any chance you might be able to rebase your branch against it at some point? (noticing it's starting to get harder to merge the current vtable wip you have into the rvkms base branch</p>",
